snippet.title: Tower of The Wizard Gameplay
snippet.description:
PLAY FOR FREE: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.suhail.wizardtower&hl=en

This is gameplay footage of various challenges in Tower of The Wizard: Gameboy Adventure. 

Does not include the insane boss fight at the end (I didn't want to spoil it :) )
